precis:
Enactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN
LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (DAWSON FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides
for the withdrawal from disposal of specific tracts of land in the Yukon
Territory in order to facilitate the settlement of land claims made by the
Dawson First Nation.
